<main data-rocket-location-hash="c97c40b85ebcabe2715d1bd4d78902fc">
    <a name="skip_to_main_content" id="skip_to_main_content" class="skip">Main Content</a>
<header data-rocket-location-hash="017994fdb5bb8e5a4270fd4455a13d9f" class="page-header page-header--page page-header--nothing-featured"><div data-rocket-location-hash="4ef5eb426b322978f600fc54c18ea168" class="breadcrumb_wrapper"><ul id="breadcrumbs" class="breadcrumbs" aria-label="breadcrumbs" role="menubar"><li class="item-home" role="menuitem"><a class="bread-link bread-home" href="https://hes.wfu.edu" aria-label="Back to home"><i class="fa fa-home"></i></a></li><span>TOPS</span></div></ul>            <h1 class="general-top-page-h1">TOPS</h1>
    </header><div data-rocket-location-hash="ad0d0d9caad992a98cde7a0ed92e0e39" class="container">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full is-resized"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="712" height="359" src="https://prod.wp.cdn.aws.wfu.edu/sites/504/2024/07/TOPSlogo.png" alt="TOPS logo (red apple is the letter o), image of a knee. THE OSTEOARTHRITIS PREVENTION STUDY" class="wp-image-5052" style="width:459px;height:auto" srcset="https://prod.wp.cdn.aws.wfu.edu/sites/504/2024/07/TOPSlogo.png 712w, https://prod.wp.cdn.aws.wfu.edu/sites/504/2024/07/TOPSlogo-300x151.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 712px) 100vw, 712px" /></figure>



<div data-rocket-location-hash="2da7a20d9246c9605c230becd1bc3db7" style="height:20px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Principal Investigator:</h2>



<p>Stephen P. Messier, PhD</p>



<div data-rocket-location-hash="a44ec4c46af7f66e22747b9dc9404e4d" style="height:20px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Objective:</h2>



<p>The objective of this Phase III, multi-site (Boston, MA, Chapel Hill, NC, Sydney, Australia, and Winston-Salem, NC) randomized clinical trial is to establish the efficacy of an intervention of dietary weight loss, exercise, and weight-loss maintenance for knee OA prevention.</p>



<div data-rocket-location-hash="4b7401ee17f853c298d575de9f03492d" style="height:20px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Site Principal Investigators:</h2>



<div data-rocket-location-hash="ca17ea653251e4986792dba158c788ac" class="wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex">
<div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="460" height="120" src="https://prod.wp.cdn.aws.wfu.edu/sites/504/2024/07/WFUlogo_TOPS-5-120x460-1.png" alt="Wake Forest University logo" class="wp-image-5053" srcset="https://prod.wp.cdn.aws.wfu.edu/sites/504/2024/07/WFUlogo_TOPS-5-120x460-1.png 460w, https://prod.wp.cdn.aws.wfu.edu/sites/504/2024/07/WFUlogo_TOPS-5-120x460-1-300x78.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 460px) 100vw, 460px" /></figure>



<p><strong>Site PI:&nbsp;</strong>Shannon Mihalko, PhD</p>



<div style="height:10px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full is-resized"><img decoding="async" width="444" height="236" src="https://prod.wp.cdn.aws.wfu.edu/sites/504/2024/07/Screenshot-2024-07-19-at-12.22.10%E2%80%AFPM.png" alt="" class="wp-image-5079" style="width:140px;height:auto" srcset="https://prod.wp.cdn.aws.wfu.edu/sites/504/2024/07/Screenshot-2024-07-19-at-12.22.10%E2%80%AFPM.png 444w, https://prod.wp.cdn.aws.wfu.edu/sites/504/2024/07/Screenshot-2024-07-19-at-12.22.10%E2%80%AFPM-300x159.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 444px) 100vw, 444px" /></figure>



<p><strong>Site PI:&nbsp;</strong>Elena Losina, PhD, MSc</p>
</div>



<div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="460" height="120" src="https://prod.wp.cdn.aws.wfu.edu/sites/504/2024/07/UNClogoTOPS-2-120x460-1-1.png" alt="UNC Chapel Hill logo" class="wp-image-5054" srcset="https://prod.wp.cdn.aws.wfu.edu/sites/504/2024/07/UNClogoTOPS-2-120x460-1-1.png 460w, https://prod.wp.cdn.aws.wfu.edu/sites/504/2024/07/UNClogoTOPS-2-120x460-1-1-300x78.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 460px) 100vw, 460px" /></figure>



<p><strong>Site PI:&nbsp;</strong>Leigh Callahan, PhD</p>



<div style="height:10px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="301" height="50" src="https://prod.wp.cdn.aws.wfu.edu/sites/504/2024/07/WFU-School-of-Medicine-Header.png" alt="Wake Forest University School of Medicine logo" class="wp-image-5057" /></figure>



<p><strong>Data Coordinating Center:</strong>&nbsp;Edward Ip, PhD</p>
</div>



<div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="460" height="120" src="https://prod.wp.cdn.aws.wfu.edu/sites/504/2024/07/sydneyTOPSlogo-2-120x460-1.png" alt="University of Sydney logo" class="wp-image-5055" srcset="https://prod.wp.cdn.aws.wfu.edu/sites/504/2024/07/sydneyTOPSlogo-2-120x460-1.png 460w, https://prod.wp.cdn.aws.wfu.edu/sites/504/2024/07/sydneyTOPSlogo-2-120x460-1-300x78.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 460px) 100vw, 460px" /></figure>



<p><strong>Site PI:&nbsp;</strong>David Hunter, MD</p>



<div style="height:10px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="460" height="120" src="https://prod.wp.cdn.aws.wfu.edu/sites/504/2024/07/MUstacked120x460.png" alt="University of Missouri Mizzou logo" class="wp-image-5058" srcset="https://prod.wp.cdn.aws.wfu.edu/sites/504/2024/07/MUstacked120x460.png 460w, https://prod.wp.cdn.aws.wfu.edu/sites/504/2024/07/MUstacked120x460-300x78.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 460px) 100vw, 460px" /></figure>



<p><strong>Data Coordinating Center:&nbsp;</strong>Jimi Cook, DVM, PhD, OTSC</p>
</div>
</div>



<div data-rocket-location-hash="7486756f26dab649ff0acbee83878671" style="height:20px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Co-Investigators:</h2>



<p>Ali&nbsp;Guermazi, MD, PhD,&nbsp;Jeffery Katz, MD, MSc,&nbsp;Emily Leary, PhD,&nbsp;Richard&nbsp;Loeser&nbsp;Jr., MD, Gary Miller, R.D. PhD,&nbsp;Brian&nbsp;Pietrosimone, PhD, ATC, Sandra Soto, PhD, Kurt Spindler, MD, Ezequiel Zamora, MD</p>



<div data-rocket-location-hash="6b71b4c7877e07452efb34c4125f2d7a" style="height:20px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Interested in Participating?</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>Study participants receive, at no cost:</strong></h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>A 48-month healthy lifestyle program</li>



<li>Classes may include a combination of weight loss, healthy lifestyle, nutrition, and exercise</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>You may qualify to participate if you:&nbsp;</strong></h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Are female and at least 50 years of age</li>



<li>Are overweight</li>



<li>Have little to no knee pain</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Contact us:</h3>



<p><em>To learn more, please call 877-238-4825, option 6; email us at&nbsp;<a href="mailto:tops@wfu.edu" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">tops@wfu.edu</a>;</em><br /><em>or visit&nbsp;<a href="https://redcap.link/jp42mvpo" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">https://redcap.link/jp42mvpo</a>&nbsp;to see if you qualify</em></p>



<div data-rocket-location-hash="57cdfc52514c229240b81171ba5dbf8b" style="height:20px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<div data-rocket-location-hash="8884daf974ce4da0d071b783b9553431" style="height:20px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



